    "created_at": "2018-10-25T23:08:17Z",
    "updated_at": "2018-10-25T23:08:17Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I was able, with @avalach21 and @Baxxster's help, to track this down to a race condition between server connection (which automatically runs immediately after startup on mod-switch) and the LocalProfile-forum validation.\r\n\r\nIf https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/b815e80e992c96a57f1a83932317593130eae7a9/OpenRA.Game/LocalPlayerProfile.cs#L171 runs (on the main thread) before https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/b815e80e992c96a57f1a83932317593130eae7a9/OpenRA.Game/LocalPlayerProfile.cs#L102 (on the download thread) then the issue here will be triggered.\r\n\r\nA simple repro case is to add `Thread.Sleep(5000);` at the start of `onQueryComplete` in `LocalPlayerProfile.RefreshPlayerData`."
  },
